						<h2 class="page-heading-md font-weight-extrabold line-height-heading-1 color-spacesuit-white-important">What Did Hubble See on Your Birthday?</h2>
						<p class="p-lg margin-top-2 padding-0 margin-bottom-4 color-spacesuit-white-important">Hubble explores the universe 24 hours a day, 7 days a week. That means it has observed some fascinating cosmic wonder every day of the year, including on your birthday.</p>
